but I play on-hit teemo...so I actually build AS items and always max E first XD
{{item:3153}} {{item:3085}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3091}} {{item:3022}} {{item:3252}} 
Shred resistances, % hp damage, near AS cap (it does cap with passive after stealth), slows, and does it to 3 targets at a time...and the poison DoT to boot. Mallet and Wits are semi-defensive choices and the lifesteal from BotRK means I can survive fights while making teamfights fun...and splitpush OP.  I love playing Teemo and don't understand why people hate him so much.
